column8:
The record breaking Vostok Rocket. This mighty piece of Soviet rocketry helped set five records:

It carried Yuri Gagarin, the first ever man in space - The first manned mission lasting a full 24 hrs - The first simultaneous flight of two manned spacecraft - The longest solo orbital flight - The first woman in space.

Designed by the great Sergei Korolev the Chief Designer, the Vostok rocket will forever remain part of man's first ever steps into space.
